arStrings.szText: "Here, I hope these give you some answers."
Ah, these will do perfectly. Thank you for your diligence.
All of these elements thrum with the same magic. The mages clearly intended their spells to persist through the generations.
While these creatures are certainly brutal, I find what the Ennead clan did here quite unsavory. If you'd follow me, there's something I'd like to show you.
